comments: Holiday (MIL) brings his arm toward Cunningham's (DET) front and marginal contact occurs during Cunningham's drive.
Matthews (MIL) places his hand momentarily on Bogdanovic's (DET) hip before correcting.
Matthews (MIL) brushes Cunningham's (DET) arm as he is gathering the ball, and marginal contact occurs as Cunningham spins away from the contact in the lane.
Stewart (DET) brushes Portis' (MIL) arm and marginal contact occurs as Portis secures the rebound.
Stewart (DET) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact from Antetokounmpo (MIL) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
As Bogdanovic (DET) jumps for the rebound, he momentarily places his hand on Lopez's (MIL) shoulder before immediately removing his hand as Lopez reaches for the rebound.
Holiday (MIL) extends his forearm into Ivey's (DET) path and initiates contact that affects Ivey's SQBR.
Cunningham (DET) and Matthews (MIL) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Lopez (MIL) briefly grasps Bey's (DET) arm and immediately releases his arm as the post entry pass is being delivered.
Bey (DET) applies a stayed hand to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) side, and the contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Stewart (DET) brushes Lopez's (MIL) arm as they pursue the rebound.
Stewart (DET) is already in Holiday's (MIL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Cunningham (DET) does not bring part of his hand under the ball when he brings his dribble to a pause.
Lopez (MIL) applies his forearm to Stewart's (DET) upper body, and he absorbs the marginal contact as he defends the shot near the rim.
Lopez (MIL) brings his hands toward Ivey (DET) and marginal contact occurs as Lopez releases away to roll.
Matthews (MIL) and Bogdanovic (DET) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Bey (DET) establishes himself in Holiday's (MIL) path with two hands against his back, and Bey collapses his arms to his chest as he absorbs the marginal contact.
Stewart (DET) is already in Holiday's (MIL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Lopez (MIL) briefly grasps Stewart's (DET) arm and marginal contact occurs during the rebounding sequence.
Ivey (DET) brushes Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm and marginal contact occurs in transition.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) brings his arm towards Cunningham's (DET) side and marginal contact occurs as Antetokounmpo spins towards the basket.
Stewart (DET) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Cunningham (DET) applies a stayed hand to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) side and marginal contact occurs as Antetokounmpo loses control of the ball on his own.
Matthews (MIL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Bogdanovic (DET).
After the ball is deflected by Matthews (MIL), Bogdanovic (DET) legally regains possession to begin his dribble.
Matthews (MIL) is moving alongside Bogdanovic's (DET) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) legally contests Cunningham's (DET) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Bey (DET) commits a take foul on Lopez (MIL).
